4. Desigh a trigger which will be fired when a new record is inserted or update for the following conditions: 
a. salary should be more than 10000 for category 1
b. salary should be more than 20000 focategory 2
c. salary should be more than 3000 for category 3 :-


CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER trg_salary_check
BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE ON emp
FOR EACH ROW
BEGIN
    IF :NEW.category = 1 AND :NEW.salary <= 10000 THEN
        RAISE_APPLICATION_ERROR(-20001, 'Salary must be > 10000 for category 1');

    ELSIF :NEW.category = 2 AND :NEW.salary <= 28000 THEN
        RAISE_APPLICATION_ERROR(-20002, 'Salary must be > 20000 for category 2');

    ELSIF :NEW.category = 3 AND :NEW.salary <= 10000 THEN
        RAISE_APPLICATION_ERROR(-20003, 'Salary must be > 10000 for category 3');
    END IF;
END;
/

